				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13400489/scp-4764#post-4675747</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2020 04:36:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Silly Half Orc</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6027596</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Basically submission end on the 21rst and the voting period on the 28th. The two aren't mutually exclusive. The voting period last longer than the submission period to provide a chance for later submissions to the contest.</p> <p>At least that is my understanding</p> 
				 	]]>
