					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13400489#post-4674487</guid>
				<title>Site Criticism Team - Staff Review</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13400489/scp-4764#post-4674487</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 02 Jun 2020 23:24:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TheMightyMcB</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4483018</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Crit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Crit</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p>Rate of bombardment is not to fall under 30 direct strikes per 24-hour period.</p> </blockquote> <p>Missing &quot;The&quot; at the start.</p> <blockquote> <p>If bombardment ceases for longer than one hour at any time, and bombardment cannot be re-initiated</p> </blockquote> <p>No comma.</p> <blockquote> <p>Mobile Task Force Omega-12 (&quot;Achilles' Heels&quot;) is authorized to physically engage SCP-4764, via basic wrestling techniques and hand-to-hand combat.</p> </blockquote> <p>No comma.</p> <blockquote> <p>high-G note</p> </blockquote> <p>Nitpick but you could say which g it is by denoting the octave, e.g. G4 or G5.</p> <blockquote> <p>brown-ish</p> </blockquote> <p>Not sure i like the use of this in a clinical file.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Overall, this is just good fun. It's basically exactly what I'd imagine anartist punks to do, I love it. +1.</p> <p><span style="font-size:smaller;"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> <em>Opinions expressed in this review do not reflect the opinions of SCP Wiki staff as a whole. Please respond to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591140249" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span> or contact the captain of the Site Criticism Team, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591140249" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span>, for any questions or concerns relating to this review.</em></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
