uño</a><br /> <strong>Release year:</strong> 2014</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><strong>Source:</strong> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=24410753">wikimedia commons</a>, <a href="https://pixabay.com/vectors/head-skull-bones-skeleton-death-2026397/">Pixabay</a> &amp; the SCP-Wiki<br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC BY 3.0<br /> <strong>Title:</strong> peopleschoice.jpg<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Heflox">Heflox</a>, <a href="https://pixabay.com/users/OpenClipart-Vectors-30363/">OpenClipart-Vectors</a>, &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591410842" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span><br /> <strong>Release year:</strong> 2020</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><strong>Source:</strong> SCP-Wiki<br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC BY 3.0<br /> <strong>Title:</strong> jojonote.jpg<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591410842" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span><br /> <strong>Release year:</strong> 2020</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>The line &quot;If you fuckin' wankers don't get your shit FLYIN' I'm gonna go back in time and fuck all of your ancestors until your DNA is 70% my spunk!&quot; is partially attributed to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591410842" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" >ProcyonLotor</a></span></p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>The character of Streiborg was inspired by real-life punk legend <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GG_Allin">GG Allin</a>.</p> </blockquote> <p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1782920&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591410842" alt="Oboebandgeek99" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1782920)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" >Oboebandgeek99</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591410842" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187161&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591410842" alt="plaidypus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187161)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaidypus" >plaidypus</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591410842" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" >cybersqyd</a></span> for critiquing this travesty before I posted it. I'm sorry.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
